text: Subhash Sudha is an Indian politician. He was elected to the Haryana Legislative Assembly from Thanesar in the 2019 Haryana Legislative Assembly election as a member of the Bharatiya Janata Party.Myneta ==References== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Haryana Legislative Assembly Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians from Haryana Category:People from Kurukshetra district Category:Haryana MLAs 2019– Category:Haryana MLAs 2014–2019 Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
